comments:
Major errors

The disease mechanistic link is off: Hajdu-Cheney is typically linked to NOTCH2 truncations with gain-of-function, so using a KO phenotype as a direct explanation is likely incorrect.

Improvement Comments: 
- rule out segmentation artifacts for extreme spreading; 
- model at well/plate level; 
- validate focal adhesions directly (vinculin/paxillin/FAK) before committing to that mechanism.
